Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:50.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take back Sanji who \Nwas being pressed into a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:53.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,marriage and left his friends behind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:55.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others infiltrated
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:57.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the Whole Cake Island\Nwhere Emperor Big Mom is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:02.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy eliminated Sweet General Cracker\Nin the Seducing Woods
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:05.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and finally saw Sanji again,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:07.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Sanji rejected his \Nfriends' offer to regroup.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to come back, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without you, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't become the King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy stayed behind to wait for Sanji{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and clashed with the enraged army\Nthat was organized to avenge Cracker.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, in a secret meeting with Pudding,\NSanji revealed what was on his mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanna go away without hurting anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My adventure ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let your marriage with me be hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He learned Pudding's feelings\Nand made a decision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm good enough for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get married tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then Luffy finally got knocked out\Nin the battle against the enraged army.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Invading the Chateau!\NReach the Road Ponegliff!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:29.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,A GUEST ROOM WHERE SANJI STAYS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry - we should never have done this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be here waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stay safe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you came to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried\Nbecause you've been passed out all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I remember! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna free you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this possible?!\NThis won't come off no matter how much I pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's useless, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:47.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Who else could \Ndo something like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:46.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PRISON LIBRARY IN THE WHOLE CAKE CHATEAU
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why would I wanna do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! I shouldn't be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta get back to that spot\Nbefore Sanji comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck with that.\NBut you'll never be able to get out of here. Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch you alive soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat them! Let's eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Chobro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carrot, lend me your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, we're going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay, got it! That's my Chobro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you whispering about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Attack them already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?!\NThose are just reflections!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:19.20,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,TREASURE REPOSITORY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Security is very tight as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Pedro-{\i1}san{\i0}, there they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two Ponegliffs and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Road Ponegliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:52.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...there are about 30 Ponegliffs, \Ninscribed stone blocks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:53.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TREASURE REPOSITORY IN THE WHOLE CAKE CHATEAU
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:57.43,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...that have never broken for \Nover hundreds of years...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:10:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...which exist in the whole world-{\i1}bon{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And only nine of those 30 Ponegliffs\Nhave specific kinds of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take those to the \Nlast island - Raftel,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the stones will reveal the \Ntruth of this world-{\i1}soir{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do it, Sweet \NGeneral Smoothie-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have mercy on me, Smoothie-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoothie-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in order to go to the last \Nisland Raftel, you need...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...four Road Ponegliffs, the red stones!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:11:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Including the one delivered by Jimbei\Nthe other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A present for you. I got it on my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we Big Mom Pirates have two Ponegliffs
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and one Road Ponegliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means three stones in total-{\i1}vous pla√Æt{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how important those three stones are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:33.44,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE OF THE SWEET 3 GENERALS OF\N THE BIG MOM PIRATES MINISTER OF JUICE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why did you suddenly \Ntighten security now, Tamago?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I got nothing to do until the tea party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:38.82,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,C. SMOOTHIE - 14TH DAUGHTER OF THE CHARLOTTE FAMILY\NBOUNTY: 932 MILLION BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:38.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't mind guarding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you-{\i1}renaissance{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a former pirate captain\Nwho came to this island about five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a Mink Ponegliff thief\Nand it seems that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he has snuck onto this island again-{\i1}souffle{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His life was spared because his \Ncompatriot Pekoms begged for his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he return?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get all four red Road Ponegliffs,\Nyou can reach Raftel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that's the road \Nto become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a quest worthy of \Nthe Four Emperors-{\i1}bon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of Mama, we put our lives on \Nthe line to protect these stones-{\i1}chocolat{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:50.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,OUTSIDE OF THE TREASURE REPOSITORY\NIN THE WHOLE CAKE CHATEAU
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:13:02.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,SPIRITS CELLAR
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? They increased security?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they were calling her \NSweet General Smoothie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is a beautiful woman with long legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet General... That \Nmeans she's a top officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.\NNo wonder she looked strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless.\NThey now have perfect security.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no chance even at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our last hope may vanished\Nwhen Tamago noticed I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others are having difficulty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if we could \Ncomplete our mission smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was touched by what you said the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0} to become the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King of the Pirates, he'll need \Nthe Road Ponegliff someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:14:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it won't be so easy to come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, we have to clash with them head-on\Nif we really want to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we all could \Nmake it this far again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given this, maybe now is the rare chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we invade, both of us will get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Baron Tamago's target?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro-{\i1}san{\i0}, would you be \Nwilling to serve as bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:11.47,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"MIRRO-WORLD" - BRULEE'S HOUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boil, boil, boil! Boil, boil, boil!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boil, boil! Boil, boil!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobro, help! It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop whining, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't eat humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Minks could be edible so I gotta try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat me! I'm not delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Carrot go, Brulee!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a real rabbit!\NOf course, she's not delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You think so? Then, \Nmaybe I shouldn't try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:48.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! I'm too tough \Nand stinky and disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let her go.\NKeep your mouth shut, you odd reindeer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll join Mama's collection \Nof strange beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Collection of strange beasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. So just sit there quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay! We managed to get to this point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:22.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made sure to get tied up in Heavy Point
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:26.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could escape from these \Nchains instantly by transforming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving Chopper trouble!\NPedro will be mad at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been six hours since I used Monster \NPoint yesterday so I can use it already!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the delicious soup is ready,\Ndump her in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boil, boil, boil! Boil, boil, boil!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boil, boil, boil! Boil, boil, boil!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's gonna be delicious! Let's try!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boil, boil, boil! Boil, \Nboil, boil! Puff, puff!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now's the chance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boil, boil, boil! Boil, boil, boil!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boil, boil! Boil, boil!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:20.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WHOLE CAKE CHATEAU LIBRARY
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is always an infinite \Nuniverse in a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. This is a super-rare, man-eating lion\Nwhich has a human face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Manticore."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strange beast escaped \Nthat from Impel Down
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during the attack of \NBlackbeard two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loincloth, loincloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this one is my pride and joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:18:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame. But it's living in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those animals in books will never age.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it's supposed to be because \Nwhat's in a book should never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The books in this library contain\Nrare creatures from across the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what my son Montd'Or is capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, we got a Centaur from Punk Hazard
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a Griffon that we \Nfound in the South Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even got something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Long-Limbs human!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I stepped into this country,\NI've seen a wide variety of races.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:19:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Because that's the kind of country\Nthat Totto Land aspires to becoming...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one race that I don't see\Nand I couldn't stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're here, we would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Giant Tribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that all races are living in this country\Nbut I haven't seen even one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I've seen is people who \Nare bigger than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you haven't happened to run into one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just didn't get a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma... Mama... Ma, we... we... we have \Nbrought those... those two here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you excuse me? I'm very busy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather isn't so nice\Nbut have a good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I got nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the real Germa 66.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially Ichiji-{\i1}sama{\i0} and Reiju-{\i1}sama{\i0}\Nwere just as cool as I thought they'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! How foolish you are\Nto be influenced by a comic strip!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The important thing isn't how they look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've already closed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, what page was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Page 55-{\i1}fa{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,51.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:20:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,53.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,55.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two? I like the look on their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna keep us like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take a shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is covered in sticky syrup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:26.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it's so sweet, Candy-{\i1}chan{\i0}. Lick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:26.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PEROSPERO - ELDEST SON \NOF THE CHARLOTTE FAMILY
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Transponder Snail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been a while, Straw Hat Luffy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You finally made it this far.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Big Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out! I gotta go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get out of here\Neven if I have to destroy everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoa-whoa, you've still \Ngot that kind of spirit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you didn't bring the whole crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd forgotten what you said to me\Non the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll kick your ass all over the New World{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and make the Fish-Man Island my territory!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.22,0:22:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll kick your ass someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we just came to take \NSanji back this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with bluffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just gonna rot \Naway helplessly in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Straw Hat, you're already doomed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!\NIf you wanna fight, show yourself, Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fight you right here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brook and Pedro finally start creating a ruckus\Nin the Emperor's headquarters!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.36,0:23:32.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Luffy comes \Nunder hard questioning by
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.03,0:23:34.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom but he challenges her head-on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.37,0:23:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Mom erupts into volcanic rage and\Nthings are in a tense touch-and-go situation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.52,0:23:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"A Fateful Confrontation! Luffy and Big Mom!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
